{"tid":2098912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Sor9ry, 一時間很難分佢兩兄弟","createTime":"2020-07-08T00:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T00:44:23.000Z","uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a0ba77b84e6262639cb43bf911c6c8e98b36a7","tid":2098912,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"琴日, 以為「烏坎村母豬」早左落黎做酒店阿頭.<br />\n原來係Pokemon 勁寸「國家の旗」講嘢難聽粗口.<br />\n因佢兩兄弟口吻越來越似, 一時間很難分佢兩兄弟, 真係Sor9ry.<br />\n應以一個已是地中海, 另一個係地中海形成中, 來分佢兩兄弟.<br />\n<br />\n另外, 從維園出發的港島200萬+1遊行, 不會再有, <br />\n加上, 永續限聚令, 遊行已成歷史, R.I.P."},{"pid":"6847d0b1adfa1a156c74654cdb03ecf573ddabe9","tid":2098912,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:24:08.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪有末期語癌？"},{"pid":"59cf99fa2a7c8d4619d563f2479444da68751590","tid":2098912,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"太隱晦，隱晦到唔知樓主講緊邊個"},{"pid":"8b83454ecf4b5dc6f7fbf6311c144d69692eb7a9","tid":2098912,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"59cf99fa2a7c8d4619d563f2479444da68751590","tid":2098912,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"太隱晦，隱晦到唔知樓主講緊邊個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:39:26.000Z","msg":"好明顯架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283da8a76b4d689ec4f0b8f15cb7b203ffb60473","tid":2098912,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"59cf99fa2a7c8d4619d563f2479444da68751590","tid":2098912,"uid":1082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"太隱晦，隱晦到唔知樓主講緊邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"真香港人才會明"},{"pid":"d2c2a0b7da5a282d2f01e148b624aaf566473ab4","tid":2098912,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6847d0b1adfa1a156c74654cdb03ecf573ddabe9","tid":2098912,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T00